Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.64,0:00:21.45,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找尋著看不見的明天 著急地用手觸摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.60,0:00:25.95,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而受傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.10,0:00:38.54,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來是沒有出口的迷宮 就像需要解謎的拼圖一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.20,0:00:49.77,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有奇跡出現   夢想也將成為勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.01,0:00:54.98,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart  在荏苒的季節中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.09,0:00:57.86,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你的憧憬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.01,0:01:00.40,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just my Love  因為那份思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.51,0:01:03.65,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我了無形的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.93,0:01:09.77,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像稍微感受到了迷惘和煩惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.77,0:01:11.33,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論在什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.48,0:01:14.71,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart  在荏苒的季節中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.49,0:01:23.63,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just my Love  對你的思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.62,0:01:28.64,Open,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel your Heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.80,0:20:23.07,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在心中綻放的玫瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.18,0:20:29.86,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗中燃盡  僅是一束火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.15,0:20:38.54,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在滿是隔閡的街上 如遊戲般的迷失自我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.69,0:20:42.79,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以小丑的心情躊躇著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.62,0:20:51.13,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要踐踏悲傷的殘片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.29,0:20:55.51,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人在未來中戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.05,0:21:03.65,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以解開今晚的謎底仍然是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.88,0:21:08.11,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up！真面目  Hurry up！回到從前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.47,0:21:15.66,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is passion　兩個人的手中充滿的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.77,0:21:22.62,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入黑暗之中  想緊緊擁抱住陽光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.07,0:21:28.17,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Love is burning 在迷宮中相互Kiss
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.33,0:21:37.22,End,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁向樂園  僅差一道門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.70,0:00:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著時代的演進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.10,0:00:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困難的案件也與日俱增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.00,0:00:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的事情發生在卡拉OK包廂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶誕節的情歌卻是分離之歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.51,0:00:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.00,0:00:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.20,0:00:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧卻過於常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.40,0:00:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.12,0:01:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉OK包廂殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.23,0:01:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是美好的耶誕節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.70,0:01:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我的身邊卻是你們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.80,0:01:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看這句話應該由我來講才對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.20,0:01:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 新一呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.70,0:01:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是偶爾會打電話來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.01,0:01:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼有這種人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.41,0:01:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可是一年一度的耶誕節啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.41,0:01:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個推理狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.41,0:01:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看他就是在耍酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.01,0:01:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.92,0:02:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他每次都充滿了自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.82,0:02:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝模作樣 滿肚子鬼主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.52,0:02:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.20,0:02:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此他還是有優點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.92,0:02:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.13,0:02:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是園子你有心上人了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.00,0:02:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有心上人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.40,0:02:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫木村達也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.40,0:02:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.00,0:02:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在最受歡迎的那支搖滾樂隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.40,0:02:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷克斯裏面的那個木村達也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.31,0:02:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.21,0:02:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是個藝人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.91,0:02:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他的演唱會結束的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.71,0:02:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我靠著我爸爸的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.21,0:02:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以參加他們的慶功會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.21,0:02:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候就能親眼看到達也了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.02,0:02:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭你也去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.12,0:02:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能見到達也他們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.92,0:02:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是鈴木財團的大小姐呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.42,0:02:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你說 什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.12,0:02:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是下周日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.63,0:02:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.13,0:02:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.70,0:02:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.01,0:03:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確唱得不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.50,0:03:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起某個樂團唱得好聽多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.71,0:03:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 達也 你喝多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.02,0:03:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.80,0:03:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒還有個脫口秀的節目嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.92,0:03:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦 你這個醜八怪給我走開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.80,0:03:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醜八怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得過分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.90,0:03:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.83,0:03:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼可以這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.60,0:03:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻理是我們樂隊的經理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.90,0:03:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她這麼說是理所當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.60,0:03:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒要問問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.00,0:03:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身為我們的鼓手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.40,0:03:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了你應該做的事了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美江子 還有你也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.81,0:03:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天在搞什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.91,0:03:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經受夠了你那蹩腳的吉他演奏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.91,0:03:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.12,0:03:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你好久了隅井先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.42,0:03:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是我告訴我們經理要訂你們這家店的房間的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.32,0:03:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.22,0:03:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你常來照顧我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.32,0:03:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.63,0:03:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從前的樂隊領隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.43,0:03:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然開起這種不賺錢的店來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.20,0:03:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是可悲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.70,0:03:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.40,0:03:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從前的樂隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.10,0:04:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這首歌是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅鼻子的馴鹿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.91,0:04:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我剛才點的歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.91,0:04:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.61,0:04:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為你點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.01,0:04:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對上中學時還一直相信這個世界上有聖誕老人的你來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.82,0:04:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再合適也不過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.32,0:04:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.42,0:04:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這位愛擺架子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.90,0:04:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大美人經理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.20,0:04:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.93,0:04:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.43,0:04:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唱總行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.30,0:04:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了 達也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.70,0:04:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.70,0:04:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在昏暗的街道上 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.40,0:04:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}那閃閃發亮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.81,0:04:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.91,0:04:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.11,0:04:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙到底想幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.31,0:04:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.21,0:04:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表情這麼悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.22,0:04:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.92,0:04:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也來唱一首吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.62,0:04:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.30,0:05:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我親愛的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.00,0:05:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個大姐姐為什麼一面唱歌一面流淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.30,0:05:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我就要說再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.50,0:05:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對美江子還有樂隊說再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.31,0:05:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.91,0:05:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷克斯樂隊要解散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.61,0:05:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等這次巡迴演出一結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.21,0:05:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要離開樂隊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.22,0:05:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事樂隊都已經知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.72,0:05:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候就要跟這個蹩腳的鼓手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.32,0:05:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有幼稚的吉他手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.22,0:05:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及這位高高在上的經理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.23,0:05:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,統統說再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.63,0:05:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.10,0:05:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我唱的歌嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.40,0:05:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰幫我點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.91,0:05:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.81,0:05:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.11,0:05:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不快點就趕不上脫口秀節目了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.61,0:05:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.81,0:05:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想唱誰也不能阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.71,0:05:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.02,0:05:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打個電話到攝影棚去打個招呼說你會晚到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.92,0:05:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.80,0:05:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血紅的維納斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.30,0:06:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}已逝去的那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.73,0:06:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木村達也現在唱的這首歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.20,0:06:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}就是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.70,0:06:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他的暢銷曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.70,0:06:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ah somebody love…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.30,0:06:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血紅的維納斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.50,0:06:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.30,0:06:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}oh baby…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.80,0:06:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在座的人誰也沒想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.30,0:06:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後再也聽不到這首歌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.10,0:06:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}決定不了 無法選擇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了兇手之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.00,0:06:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你的愛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.30,0:06:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.91,0:06:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.52,0:06:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的歌唱得怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.22,0:06:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱得太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.12,0:06:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.02,0:06:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿一個飯團給我吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.10,0:06:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.90,0:06:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.90,0:06:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷克斯樂隊真的要解散嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.30,0:06:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.50,0:06:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會以個人身份複出的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.41,0:06:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,個人身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.30,0:06:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新歌已經做好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.61,0:06:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.61,0:06:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經做好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.41,0:06:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 歌名是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.40,0:07:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌名嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.70,0:07:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌名啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.30,0:07:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.20,0:07:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.60,0:07:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫救護車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.50,0:07:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去叫救護車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.40,0:07:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒救了 他已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.30,0:07:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個味道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.50,0:07:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氰酸鉀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.10,0:07:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰下的毒手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.20,0:07:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然當著我的面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.60,0:07:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.40,0:07:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個遭到懷疑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.00,0:07:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是把料理端到房間裏來的隅井店長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.00,0:07:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位店長以前曾經跟木村達也一起組過樂隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.40,0:07:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.20,0:07:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有達也一人成了職業歌手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.00,0:07:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為了現在是大受歡迎的主唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來懷疑他因為妒嫉而犯案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.90,0:07:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.60,0:07:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他端過來的料理在場的每個人都吃過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此才把他的犯罪可能性給排除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.80,0:08:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來根據驗屍報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.70,0:08:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現被害人的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.20,0:08:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及麥克風上都檢驗出了毒物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.80,0:08:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,證實木村在吃下飯團之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.20,0:08:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手上已經沾有毒物了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.90,0:08:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把毒藥塗在了麥克風上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.70,0:08:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以木村在握了麥克風之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再拿飯團就把毒附著在飯團上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠做到這一點的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是在木村達也之前唱歌的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.60,0:08:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芝崎美江子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.00,0:08:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.70,0:08:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說你那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.30,0:08:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一面流著眼淚一面唱著一首分離的歌曲是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.50,0:08:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會你和木村達也之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.60,0:08:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾經發生過什麼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.00,0:08:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是被達也給拋棄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.10,0:08:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己不自量力而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.50,0:08:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美江子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.50,0:08:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達也他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.50,0:08:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我向他表明心意的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.70,0:08:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 美江子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.60,0:08:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我心裏已經有喜歡的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.20,0:08:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道她現在去了哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.40,0:08:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我願意等她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.70,0:08:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論等到什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.90,0:08:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.60,0:09:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠等下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.20,0:09:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.20,0:09:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他告訴我不能和我交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.10,0:09:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.70,0:09:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你就這樣心生恨意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.90,0:09:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.90,0:09:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就沒有殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.91,0:09:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.51,0:09:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.61,0:09:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美江子唱的那首歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.91,0:09:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是達也一開始就擅自幫她挑選的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.11,0:09:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美江子根本就沒料到她會去唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.91,0:09:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不知道達也會跟在她後面唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.12,0:09:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以美江子絕對不可能在麥克風上塗毒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.39,0:09:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得也有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.19,0:09:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達也哥哥唱的那首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.90,0:09:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血紅的維納斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.60,0:09:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰幫他點的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.40,0:09:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達也哥哥每次唱歌的時候都會把上衣脫掉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.00,0:09:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在每次一開始唱血紅的維納斯的時候都會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.41,0:09:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.60,0:09:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.80,0:09:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達也哥哥的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.30,0:09:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼地方沾到氰酸鉀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.81,0:10:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得應該是在左手手肘的部分吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.58,0:10:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那其他人的外套呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.00,0:10:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人的外套上什麼都沒檢驗出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.10,0:10:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.90,0:10:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.80,0:10:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手讓木村達也中毒的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.70,0:10:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.70,0:10:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠使用這個方法的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.80,0:10:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是跟木村達也都穿著同樣外套的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.50,0:10:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那三個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.40,0:10:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈吉他的姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個經理姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.41,0:10:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經跟達也哥哥吵架過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.61,0:10:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們經常這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.80,0:10:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.20,0:10:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次一有什麼事情就會吵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.10,0:10:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.00,0:10:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次故意挑釁的人也幾乎都是達也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.80,0:10:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是達也所說的那麼壞的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.69,0:10:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既聰明又很認真 雖然是個大美人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.29,0:10:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻從來沒有緋聞發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.40,0:10:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.60,0:10:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.50,0:10:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是放在木村達也辦公室櫃子裏的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.00,0:11:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像裏面沒有什麼可當作線索的東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.31,0:11:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.14,0:11:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樂隊的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.68,0:11:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是叫人懷念啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.20,0:11:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是達也在成為職業歌手以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.90,0:11:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和整個樂隊一起拍的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.98,0:11:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在還留在音樂世界裏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.69,0:11:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只剩下達也和她兩個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.39,0:11:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這個樂隊出身的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.39,0:11:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了達也哥哥還有別人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.59,0:11:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那邊的那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.30,0:11:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實這是達也的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.20,0:11:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是和她在一起達也也就不想當職業歌手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.20,0:11:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這張照片上沒有拍出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.10,0:11:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 就是這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.71,0:11:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樣子變了很多倒是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.50,0:11:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.00,0:11:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她跟現在比起來確實改變了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.60,0:11:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片後面有字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.40,0:11:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再借我看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.70,0:11:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.00,0:11:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太悲慘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.90,0:11:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個案件太悲慘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.10,0:12:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道兇手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.70,0:12:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.20,0:12:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.40,0:12:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件調查統統停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.10,0:12:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把相關人員一起帶到命案現場去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.74,0:12:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.45,0:12:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經回到這裏來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.90,0:12:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.70,0:12:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭你很清楚的 那個名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.70,0:12:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是工藤新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.66,0:12:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直行蹤不明的新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.30,0:12:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.20,0:12:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.80,0:12:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思讓大家特地趕來這裏集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.40,0:12:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.60,0:12:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工藤新一一定是從這個攝影機偷看這裏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園子 借我看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.30,0:12:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裏啊 新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.50,0:13:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我就開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.30,0:13:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解開這次事件的謎團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.00,0:13:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.20,0:13:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有點奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.95,0:13:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼從剛才一開始就一直放這首歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.60,0:13:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這首是"紅鼻子的馴鹿" 目暮警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.50,0:13:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶誕節期間到處都可以聽到的聖誕歌曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.40,0:13:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這首歌也是引起兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.60,0:13:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對達也產生憤怒的歌曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.80,0:13:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說兇手就是在剛才卡拉OK的時候唱了這首歌的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.60,0:13:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.40,0:13:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了木村先生的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.10,0:13:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經理寺原麻理小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.30,0:13:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.40,0:13:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經理把達也給…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.90,0:13:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.80,0:13:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.40,0:13:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在達也倒下去的時候剛好去打電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不在這房間裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.90,0:13:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你離開了但是毒早就下好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.06,0:13:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後只要讓他唱這首歌就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.60,0:13:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這首歌是達也的暢銷曲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.90,0:13:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血紅的維納斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.00,0:13:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 你也來唱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.00,0:14:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我替你準備的麥克風來唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.70,0:14:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然麥克風上沒有塗毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.50,0:14:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.10,0:14:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唱就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.70,0:14:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣能讓你滿意的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.90,0:14:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.70,0:14:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不脫掉上衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.60,0:14:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱這首歌的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.40,0:14:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達也先生不是每次都會把上衣脫掉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.90,0:14:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說得沒錯吧 各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.70,0:14:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.50,0:14:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請從頭開始唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.00,0:14:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 提醒你一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.70,0:14:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.10,0:14:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}已逝去的那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.10,0:14:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}就是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.60,0:14:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ah somebody love…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.00,0:14:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.30,0:14:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.40,0:14:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}決定不了 無法選擇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.90,0:14:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她以前是我們樂隊的成員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.60,0:14:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我們樂隊有兩個主唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.70,0:14:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你的愛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.40,0:15:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}誰都無法知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.00,0:15:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}oh love you…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.20,0:15:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說那個經理嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.80,0:15:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.80,0:15:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下子你滿意了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.00,0:15:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.50,0:15:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你吃我為你準備的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.90,0:15:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.70,0:15:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那時達也吃飯團一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.20,0:15:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 隨便吃哪個都行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.10,0:15:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你吃完之後我們再往下談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.00,0:15:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要吃呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.10,0:15:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃那個幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.70,0:15:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在達也倒下來的時候曾經碰過他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然他的手上跟衣服上都沾有毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.10,0:15:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我的手說不定也在那時沾上了毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.80,0:15:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.30,0:15:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在麻煩你檢查一下她脫下來的那件外套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.10,0:15:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢查外套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.70,0:15:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外套上面也一樣有毒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.60,0:15:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我碰了達也之後就把外套穿上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.30,0:15:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算上面沾有毒的話也不能當作證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.60,0:16:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.00,0:16:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要警官查的其實並不是毒物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.60,0:16:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打火機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.90,0:16:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是達也當時遺失的打火機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.50,0:16:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.30,0:16:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件外套其實不是她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.50,0:16:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她為了毀滅證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.80,0:16:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意調換的達也的外套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.70,0:16:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她在一開始的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.20,0:16:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在達也外套的內側
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.30,0:16:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手手肘的地方塗了毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只要一穿上外套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.40,0:16:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面的衣服及手肘的部分就會沾上有毒的氰酸鉀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.60,0:16:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後她點了這首"血紅的維納斯"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.10,0:16:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達也他在不知情的情況下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.80,0:16:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫掉了外套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.70,0:16:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後右手碰到了沾有毒的左手肘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.40,0:16:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.30,0:16:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管他吃下什麼東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.30,0:16:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會毒發身亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.40,0:16:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.20,0:16:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼她會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.80,0:17:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的動機就在桌上這張照片裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.80,0:17:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張就是過去達也還在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.40,0:17:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長的樂隊時拍的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.80,0:17:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這照片有什麼不對勁嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.20,0:17:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了店長以外就沒別人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個的 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.30,0:17:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也在裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.70,0:17:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她跟達也一起在照片的中央
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.60,0:17:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.10,0:17:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.30,0:17:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張照片裏的她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.80,0:17:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是主要的殺人動機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.10,0:17:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.30,0:17:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我整過容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.40,0:17:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全是為了達也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.40,0:17:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從加入樂隊後就很喜歡達也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.80,0:17:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此在他成為職業歌手以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.00,0:17:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做經理也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.20,0:17:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.10,0:17:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到他這麼說我真的很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.70,0:17:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定他也對我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.00,0:17:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是因為這個才去整容的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.20,0:17:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望做一個配得上達也的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.90,0:18:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但在我整容以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.60,0:18:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的態度就完全轉變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.70,0:18:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老是在大家面前叫我醜八怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.50,0:18:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每當那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.40,0:18:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他都會叫我唱"紅鼻子的馴鹿"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.80,0:18:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達也點這首歌叫她唱 原來是這個原因啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.70,0:18:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實他一開始就是為了羞辱我才叫我當經理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.70,0:18:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我絕對不能原諒他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.90,0:18:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我太愛他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.50,0:18:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能原諒他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的 麻理小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.20,0:18:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實達也先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.20,0:18:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從很早以前就一直深愛著你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.50,0:18:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你少胡說八道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.00,0:18:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懂什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.10,0:18:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.40,0:18:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說的話都是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.40,0:18:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警官 把那張照片給我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.20,0:18:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是達也為真正喜歡的你所寫的情歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.80,0:18:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(歌名：想傳達給真實的你)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.70,0:18:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不要騙我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.90,0:18:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有騙你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.70,0:18:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是達也他這次要出的新歌裏面的歌詞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.30,0:18:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那小子每次嘴邊上總是會提到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.20,0:19:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻理她幹嘛那麼在乎別人的眼光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.50,0:19:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她為什麼要為了我去整容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.22,0:19:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是達也每次在我面前...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.70,0:19:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他這個人向來是口是心非的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.10,0:19:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想他一定是希望你變回原來的樣子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.90,0:19:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟…竟然有這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.10,0:19:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.30,0:19:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在她回來之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.50,0:19:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會一直等下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.80,0:19:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該這麼說 很抱歉 美江子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.70,0:19:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有喜歡的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.80,0:19:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達也說的喜歡的人原來是麻理經理啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.80,0:19:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.80,0:19:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.90,0:19:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.20,0:19:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個隱藏了真心的青年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.10,0:19:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟一個隱藏了面容的女子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.90,0:20:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣錯過了幸福 寫下了悲劇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.00,0:20:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在她悲傷的哭聲和眼淚中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.20,0:20:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有那張照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.90,0:20:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還在悲傷地笑著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.30,0:21:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.30,0:21:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是你以工藤新一的名義來破案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.50,0:21:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以為你已經回到家裏 她已經在那裏等了3個小時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.80,0:21:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是很想幫你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.80,0:22:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是現在這個情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.20,0:22:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就幫不上什麼忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.30,0:22:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.20,0:22:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一 你在裏面嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.80,0:22:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.00,0:22:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 你在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.20,0:22:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在的話就回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.00,0:22:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停電了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.50,0:22:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.80,0:22:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.80,0:22:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.80,0:22:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.60,0:22:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我終於回到這裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.90,0:22:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.20,0:22:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 好好的哭甚麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.70,0:22:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的這麼想見我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.20,0:22:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰想見你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.00,0:22:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我見到你真的很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.50,0:22:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.90,0:22:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於可以看到你這副傻樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.90,0:23:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這話什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.20,0:23:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必須得走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.30,0:23:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來的那件案子還沒有理出頭緒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.50,0:23:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.20,0:23:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.10,0:23:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.20,0:23:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是送你的聖誕禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.90,0:23:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滿懷感激地收下吧 新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.90,0:23:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你應該不會再瞎操心了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.60,0:23:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.50,0:23:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了 她來了 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.90,0:23:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽來接你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.00,0:23:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.60,0:23:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,江戶川柯南怎麼可能有媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.10,0:23:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博…博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.30,0:24:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.20,0:24:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個戴面具的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.70,0:24:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.10,0:24:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.50,0:24:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,江戶川柯南誘拐事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.80,0:24:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.00,0:24:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暗夜公爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.80,0:24:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕快樂 然後過個好年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.80,0:24:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明年會更精彩哦
